 
<p>
The wrecker's officials approved plans for coal mining which failed to
uphold environmental requirements.  Environmentalists sued, and
Biden's officials defended the wrecker's plan.
<p>
Fortunately, a court ruled against the plans, but why defend those
plans?  Whether or not they were lawful, 
<a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/2022/08/04/applause-court-rejects-trump-era-coal-plan-defended-biden-administration">they were clearly bad.</a>

 